Class SimpleObstacle

java.lang.Object
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.Obstacle.Obstacle
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.Obstacle.SimpleObstacle
public class SimpleObstacle
extends Obstacle
SimpleObstacle is a class that extends Obstacle which contains the attributes of a simple obstacle.

Simple obstacles are obstacles that are destroyed after 1 hit with no extra effect.
